headline: Zoetis (ZTS): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q4 Earnings?
summary: Over the past six months, Zoetis’s shares (currently trading at $166) have posted a disappointing 9.6% loss, well below the S&P 500’s 7.6% gain. This was partly driven by its softer quarterly results and might have investors contemplating their next move.
